{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"52252d77a5","title":"停战谈判不要提赔偿等问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"68750ea9bd","index":0,"year":1951,"month":7,"day":9,"articleId":"52252d77a5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"e37459bb63","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东给朝鲜民主主义人民共和国首相金日成，中央人民政府外交部副部长、朝鲜停战谈判中国人民志愿军代表团负责人李克农的电报。"},{"id":"f8072b50cd","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"解方，当时任中国人民志愿军参谋长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5dc6cb2a8c","type":"title","text":"停战谈判不要提赔偿等问题！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"e37459bb63","type":"paragraph","text":"金日成同志、李克农同志，并彭德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"f8072b50cd","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）不要提赔偿问题，因为这样提出，一则可使英、法、美团结起来而不能孤立美国：二则美国可以发救济费的办法来作答复，而北朝鲜是不能接受美国的救济费的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"984f92a962","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）如果金日成同志认为交换难民对北朝鲜不利，则可将南北朝鲜交换难民一项条文取消不要提出，但应准备南朝鲜提出此项问题时的对策。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"225fcac775","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）第二条中关于非武装区的民政事宜，同意写至“恢复一九五O年六月二十五日以前的状态”为止，以下两句可删去。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"bd54ed7a73","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）不必提出“禁止转交武器”的条件。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"db344914e6","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）同意增加解方为代表。朝中两方的代表均应用真姓名，不要用假名。并须于本日（七月九日）发表公报，叙述人民军和志愿军的代表的官阶和姓名，请克农即刻起草发金及我","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"c95c5b8b73","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"},{"id":"d5604e2eb7","type":"paragraph","text":"七月九日上午一时","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5"}],"page":{"id":"4cbf7d5054","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"52252d77a5","start":426,"end":426}}}},"__N_SSG":true}